snippet.title: Pix Hop - Gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Pix Hop is now on Google Play!
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bnoogames.pixhop

Pix Hop, a simple endless platform game. You control a bouncy white square collecting coins and avoiding lovely colored enemies.

Visit: https://bnoogames.weebly.com/pixhop
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/bnoogames
Follow us on Facebook: https://facebook.com/bnoogames

Trailer by: Abd-Alrahman Al-Sayed
Voiced by: Shady24z (https://goo.gl/AfAvQs)
